The paper deals with algorithms and experiments in machine learning, specifically in defining analogical dissimilarity between objects, which is a problem in pattern recognition and classification. This makes it likely to belong to the sub-categories of machine learning (cs.LG), artificial intelligence (cs.AI), data mining (cs.DM), computational linguistics (cs.CL), and computer vision (cs.CV).
